《'''100年：你永遠不會看到的電影'''》（{{lang-en|''100 Years: The Movie You Will Never See''}}）是一部2115年[[法國|法國]]電影，由[[勞勃·羅里葛茲|勞勃·羅里葛茲]]執導。《100年》預計於[[2115年|2115年]][[11月18日|11月18日]]上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/john-malkovich-robert-rodriguez-100-years-1201644846/|title=John Malkovich and Robert Rodriguez Made a Movie That Won’t Release Until 2115|author=Jacob Bryant|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2016-01-01|archive-date=2017-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120190614/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/john-malkovich-robert-rodriguez-100-years-1201644846/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://io9.gizmodo.com/john-malkovich-and-robert-rodriguez-have-made-a-movie-n-1743390289|title=John Malkovich and Robert Rodriguez Have Made A Movie No One Will See For 100 Years|author=Germain Lussier|publisher={{link-en|高客傳媒|Gawker Media|Gawker Media}}|work={{link-en|io9|io9}}|accessdate=2016-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622103029/http://io9.gizmodo.com/john-malkovich-and-robert-rodriguez-have-made-a-movie-n-1743390289|archive-date=2017-06-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

[[約翰·馬克維奇|約翰·馬克維奇]]與羅里葛茲於2015年11月宣布，他們與知名干邑白蘭地品牌{{le|路易十三 (干邑)|Louis XIII (cognac)|路易十三}}共同製作電影，創造一個來自一瓶路易十三所需要的一百年的電影靈感<ref name="people.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/article/john-malkovich-robert-rodriguez-movie-scoop-video|title=John Malkovich Explains Why He Made A Movie No One Will See|work=[[People_(magazine)|PEOPLE.com]]|accessdate=2016-01-01|archive-date=2016-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519011721/http://www.people.com/article/john-malkovich-robert-rodriguez-movie-scoop-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 [[2015年|2015年]][[11月18日|11月18日]]，馬克維奇和羅里葛茲釋出了三支不包含在正片内容的預告片，在當中，他們想像了從反烏托邦到高科技天堂的三種不同可能的未來。在電影首映前，電影將保存在一個高科技的防彈玻璃箱中，並於2115年11月18日首映。届時將會有一千名嘉賓（包括馬克維奇和羅里葛茲）會得以獲得觀影資格，並邀請他們的後裔參加<ref name="people.com" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/11/19/john-malkovich-robert-rodriguez-100-years|title=John Malkovich and Robert Rodriguez made a film that won’t be released until 2115|publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=2016-01-01|archive-date=2019-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330233216/https://ew.com/article/2015/11/19/john-malkovich-robert-rodriguez-100-years/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而電影的劇情仍處於保密狀態。<ref>{{Cite web|title='100 Years' movie casting, John Malkovich, Shuya Chang and Marko Zaror|url=https://youthpresspakistan.youthgroupltd.com/2015/11/100-years-movie-casting-john-malkovich.html|access-date=2022-03-13|date=2015-11-09|last=Butt|first=Muhammad Ali|website=Youth Press Pakistan|publisher=Youth Publishers|url-status=live|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209054017/https://youthpresspakistan.youthgroupltd.com/2015/11/100-years-movie-casting-john-malkovich.html}}</ref>

該片的保險箱於[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]和世界各地的某些城市展出，之後再放回到法國[[干邑|干邑]]的路易十三地下室保存著<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/05/05/cannes-film-festival-100-years-movie|title=Cannes to showcase John Malkovich movie no one will see for 100 years|publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=2016-05-07|archive-date=2019-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331042701/https://ew.com/article/2016/05/05/cannes-film-festival-100-years-movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

